        <Literal xml:lang="nl">Classificeert het type associatie gecodeerd door een RepresentativeAssociation. Verwachte waarden zijn de individuen: motifDimension, themeDimension, valueDimension, colorDimension, platformDimension, musicDimension, fashionDimension, iconicFigureDimension.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
    <AnnotationAssertion>
        <AnnotationProperty abbreviatedIRI="rdfs:comment"/>
        <IRI>/associationDimension</IRI>
        <Literal xml:lang="en">Classifies the kind of association. Expected values are the named individuals: motifDimension, themeDimension, valueDimension, colorDimension, platformDimension, musicDimension, fashionDimension, iconicFigureDimension.</Literal>
